title.narrative: Procurement of Family Planning Commodoties - Crown Agents

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of Family Planning Commodoties - Crown Agents) is a component of Sexual and Reproductive Health and HIV Prevention in Zimbabwe reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £14,768,283. This component benefits Zimbabwe, and works in the following sector(s): Reproductive health care, Family planning, STD control including HIV/AIDS. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-07-2012 and the end date is 30-06-2017.
